♪♪　この腕に感じたい　your soul

13
00:00:57,720 --> 00:01:00,720
♪♪　This moment I can feel
前兆到来を知る

14
00:01:00,720 --> 00:01:03,660
♪♪　このままいくぜ
I’m The Noizy Tribe

15
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:06,430
♪♪　Come with me,
come and cry with me

16
